        <node TEXT="“理想是指路明灯。没有理想，就没有坚定的方向；没有方向，就没有生活。而奋斗则是点燃理想之火的引信。”—— 列夫・托尔斯泰" ID="jIBjjZETp7" _mubu_text="%3Cspan%3E%E2%80%9C%E7%90%86%E6%83%B3%E6%98%AF%E6%8C%87%E8%B7%AF%E6%98%8E%E7%81%AF%E3%80%82%E6%B2%A1%E6%9C%89%E7%90%86%E6%83%B3%EF%BC%8C%E5%B0%B1%E6%B2%A1%E6%9C%89%E5%9D%9A%E5%AE%9A%E7%9A%84%E6%96%B9%E5%90%91%EF%BC%9B%E6%B2%A1%E6%9C%89%E6%96%B9%E5%90%91%EF%BC%8C%E5%B0%B1%E6%B2%A1%E6%9C%89%E7%94%9F%E6%B4%BB%E3%80%82%E8%80%8C%3C/span%3E%3Cspan%20class=%22%20text-color-red%22%3E%E5%A5%8B%E6%96%97%E5%88%99%E6%98%AF%E7%82%B9%E7%87%83%E7%90%86%E6%83%B3%E4%B9%8B%E7%81%AB%E7%9A%84%E5%BC%95%E4%BF%A1%3C/span%3E%3Cspan%3E%E3%80%82%E2%80%9D%E2%80%94%E2%80%94%20%E5%88%97%E5%A4%AB%E3%83%BB%E6%89%98%E5%B0%94%E6%96%AF%E6%B3%B0%3C/span%3E" STYLE="fork"/>
